title: Marcus Brigstocke - Planet Corduroy (British Comedy, 2007)
description:
Not as vicious as Frankie Boyle and not as Oxbridge as 
David Mitchell but just as much fun (if not more). 

en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Marcus_Brigstocke

Planet Corduroy is a medley of the material of a number of British 
stand-ups. 
There are bucketloads of antipathy towards Bush and Blair but also 
towards Daily Mail readers, SUV drivers and many more ...

Video length:  1:14:09
